text: Starobzhegokay () is a rural locality (an aul) and the administrative center of Starobzhegokayskoye Rural Settlement of Takhtamukaysky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 2509 as of 2018. There are 79 streets. == Geography == The aul is located on the bank of the Kuban River, 4 km west of Yablonovsky. == Ethnicity == The aul is inhabited by Circassians. == References == Category:Rural localities in Takhtamukaysky District
title: Starobzhegokay
